OL,7,FThe Welsh Government says it won't get
OL,8,Fenough money from the UK Government to
OL,9,Foffset all of the impact of higher
OL,10,FNational Insurance costs for public
OL,11,Fservices.
OL,13,FMinisters say there'll be a #36m
OL,14,Fshortfall even after they've raided
OL,15,Freserves.
OL,17,FThe UK Government says it's "boosted"
OL,18,Fthe Welsh Government's spending power
OL,19,Fby lifting limits on use of reserves
OL,20,Fon top of "a record #21bn" budget.
