OL,7,FEmployers have been paying more
OL,8,FNational Insurance Contributions
OL,9,F(NICs) since April after the
OL,10,FChancellor announced the increase in
OL,11,Fher budget last October.
OL,13,FThe UK Government had said it would
OL,14,Fensure funding for the Welsh
OL,15,FGovernment to cover the cost of the
OL,16,Fincrease for public sector
OL,17,Forganisations such as hospitals, local
OL,18,Fauthorities and schools.
