OL,7,FNow the Welsh Government says it's had
OL,8,Ffinal confirmation of the figures. It
OL,9,Fsays that the increase in NICS will
OL,10,Fcost the public sector here in Wales
OL,11,Fan extra #257m.
OL,13,FThe UK Government is providing #185m,
OL,14,Fleaving a shortfall of #72m.
OL,16,FThe Welsh Government says it will find
OL,17,Fhalf of that amount, #36m, from its
OL,18,Fown reserves. But it says that still
OL,19,Fleaves a gap of #36m.
