OL,7,FFinance Secretary, Mark Drakeford,
OL,8,Fsaid: "We're protecting our vital
OL,9,Fpublic services by using #36m from our
OL,10,Freserves to help address the National
OL,11,FInsurance shortfall left by UK
OL,12,FGovernment.
OL,14,F"The UK Government did provide
OL,15,Ffunding, but this falls short of the
OL,16,Factual costs faced by Welsh public
OL,17,Fservices, creating a multi-million-
OL,18,Fpound gap every year.
